The paper deals with the problem of maintaining maximal independent set in dynamic graphs, which is a fundamental problem in graph theory. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.AL (Computational Geometry).
